Great British Bake Off host Sue Perkins is now the favourite to replace Jeremy Clarkson on Top Gear .
A flurry of bets placed on Perkins have made her evens for the role , ahead of former X-factor presenter Dermot O'Leary who is 2-1 and British model Jodie Kidd who is third at 5-2 .
